Package edu.sjsu.assignment3

Class Appointment

java.lang.Object
edu.sjsu.assignment3.Appointment
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Appointment>
Direct Known Subclasses:
DailyAppointment, MonthlyAppointment, OnetimeAppointment
public abstract class Appointment extends Object implements Comparable<Appointment>
This is the superclass. This creates an Appointment, either a One Time Appointment, Daily Appointment, or Monthly Appointment. This superclass also implements a comparator to compare Appointments by their start date, then their end date, and finally their descriptions.

    • compareTo

      public int compareTo(Appointment other)
      Specified by:
      compareTo in interface Comparable<Appointment>
      Parameters:
      other - This is the other Appointment object being compared.
      Returns:
      This method returns the Appointment with the earliest start date if they differ. If the start dates are the same then it returns the Appointment with the earliest end date. If the end dates are the same then it returns the Appointment with the description that occurs first alphabetically.
